Modifications to make it run:


numpy dependency:
[1] local_mod_numpy.py  being added to  rtl/  directory
[2] rtl/top.py rtl/ulart.py  modified to import local_mod_numpy instead of numpy


exception at debug.py line 17 : loading 'rom.dump':
[3] rtl/bram.py  comment out import of debug


exception at top.py line 24 : loading 'rom.vmem':
[4] rtl/top.py  modified to use local_mod_no_prepare to indicate not run prepare()


exception at bram.py line 27 : loading 'rom3.vmem':
[5] copy the rom0.vmem, rom1.vmem, rom2.vmem, rom3.vmem to the samples directory


exception at bram.py line 29 : list index out of range:
[6] no modification. add 8192 to command line as an argument.


screen output with myhdl 0.10: the third line is 5524 characters long
    traceSignals(): Deprecated usage: See http://dev.myhdl.org/meps/mep-114.html
  tb = myhdl.traceSignals(top.TopBench)
